          "id": "medmcqa-06980865-1717-4a36-a03e-eb20a056d899",
          "text": "40 yr old female presented with breast lump of size 4 cm with involvement of skin and mobile palpable axillary LN, FNAC of lesion showed intrductal carcinoma. What is the initial management of for this pt?",
