          "id": "medmcqa-ad5457cd-c0a1-41da-9049-608e84f0dc1b",
          "text": "A 25 year old male presents to emergency dept. following a road traffic accident. On examination there is pelvic fracture and blood at urethral meatus. Following are true about pt except -",
