          "id": "medmcqa-42df5375-5026-4824-81fc-7c72d7a13f5a",
          "text": "A policemen foo..a a person ln ing unconscious in iglu lateral position on the road with superficial injury to the face, bruises on the right arm, and injury to the lateral aspect of right knee. Nerve most probably injured:",
