          "id": "medmcqa-55d252ed-aaa4-48ee-9d06-4b8485d3e3ae",
          "text": "After falling on the pavement, a 72-year-old woman is found to have a fracture of the radius and ulna (Colles' fracture). What is true of this fracture?",
