          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Right hepatic duct drains into segment V, VI, VII, VIII and left hepatic duct drains into segment I, II, III, IV, the segment I have an independent supply of poal and hepatic veins. Reference SRB edition :5 page:593",
          "hint": "Topic: G.I.T"
