          "id": "medmcqa-920ad252-d347-4be2-baa1-cbd1ed428f01",
          "text": "A 65-year-old male patient complains of loss of libido and is found to have a low free and total testosterone level. Treatment is commenced with testosterone supplemental therapy. What is the next step in management after testosterone administration?",
