          "explanation": "Renal transplantation is the preferred treatment for many patients with end stage renal disease (ESRD), because it provides a better quality of life for them than dialysis.\n\n\nThe most common causes of ESRD (in decreasing order) are:\n\n\nDiabetes mellitus\nHypertension\nGlomerulonephritis"
