          "id": "medmcqa-b37906c4-b3a2-493d-adf8-5ac49a26b4c3",
          "text": "A female developed a well circumscribed swelling on the nape of her neck. It is not transilluminant, painless and easily moveable. Which of the following one is NOT brilliantly transilluminant?",
